<br>
IE: Summon a pet, use the pet only (no nukes) to do damage a mob to the point where it begins to run, reclaim pet, let someone of appropriate level who isn't grouped with you kill the mob with one blow.  The killing blow will gain the XP.  However, if the pet was still alive, you would take the XP.  From memory (though somewhat fuzzy), if you have done any offensive damage, you will still gain the XP.<br>
<br>
